&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;SUMMARY&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Our Production Associate is an essential member of our team, contributing directly to the achievement of business objectives through the efficient and safe execution of various production tasks. This role involves packaging, line inspection, and the maintenance of production equipment and assemblies to ensure smooth operations and adherence to quality standards.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;SHIFT TIME&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are seeking to hire&lt;strong data-start=&quot;103&quot; data-end=&quot;130&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;Production Associates&lt;/strong&gt; to support our day-to-day operations. These team members will play a key role in maintaining production flow, ensuring product quality, and meeting operational goals in a fast-paced environment.&amp;nbsp;This is a &lt;strong data-start=&quot;195&quot; data-end=&quot;213&quot;&gt;full-time role&lt;/strong&gt; (40 hours per week), scheduled &lt;strong data-start=&quot;245&quot; data-end=&quot;270&quot;&gt;Monday - Friday&lt;/strong&gt;, with the possibility of &lt;strong data-start=&quot;296&quot; data-end=&quot;332&quot;&gt;overtime based on business needs&lt;/strong&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;This position is scheduled for a &lt;strong&gt;graveyard shift&lt;/strong&gt;, which is expected to fall between &lt;strong&gt;9:30 PM and 7:30 AM&lt;/strong&gt;. The exact working hours are still being finalized and will be confirmed during the interview process.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;SALARY&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;$20.25/per hour&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;DUTIES AND RESPONSIBILITIES&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
