&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;SUMMARY &lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The Sr. Manager, Innovation, is a key driver of Daiya’s growth agenda. Reporting to the Director of Innovation &amp;amp; Insights, this role owns the end-to-end commercialization of our innovation pipeline - translating high-potential ideas into successful, consumer-centric product launches.&amp;nbsp; This leader sets the commercial product agenda, aligns cross-functional stakeholders around clear priorities, and secures the organizational focus and resources required to win.&amp;nbsp; Day-to-day, the Sr. Manager orchestrates cross-functional delivery with rigor and pace -&amp;nbsp; shaping product development, packaging design, business cases,&amp;nbsp; learning plans, and integrated go-to-market strategies to ensure every launch lands with impact.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;JOB RESPONSIBILITIES&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Lead the Development of Innovation Projects&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Build a forward-looking, multi-year pipeline of business-driving ideas and projects grounded in consumer insights, category dynamics, and market opportunities&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Partner with Insights &amp;amp; Ideation to translate high-potential concepts into defined projects with clear priorities, success criteria, strategic objectives.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Oversee projects through the stage-gate process, including establishing the scope of the project, and partnering with Project Management to ensure projects meet key milestones and objectives&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Lead and influence cross-functional teams to advance innovation with pace - providing direction on priorities and briefs, simplifying complex problems &amp;amp; making decisions at critical project junctures&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Manage the learning plan and understand methodologies to deepen consumer understanding and derive new insights, optimize new launches, and validate project action standards&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Lead the Commercialization &amp;amp; Launch of New Platforms &amp;amp; Products:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Oversee commercialization plans, including partnering with Sales team to develop winning strategies at the customer level and category level&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Parter with Insights, Category Management, and Business Development to create compelling sales stories that secure distribution on new launches&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Serving as key expert/resource for marketing, sales, and customers.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Support &amp;amp; participate in development of communications briefs on new launches, ensuring consumer insight and business and marketing objectives are accurately captured and addressed through integrated communication plan development&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Deliver Business Results&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Develop and manage a pipeline of projects that delivers against Innovation growth targets while strengthening brand equity and overall business performance.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Own the P&amp;amp;L for new launches, ensuring projects meet financial criteria for commercialization&lt;/li&gt;
